s\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bigham\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1726}, {\"ngram\": \"his decision\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1747}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's more just how I see performance.\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1802, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"performance\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1801}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How I want to do performance is not particularly aligned with how Ineos wanted to go about it.\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1897, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1869, \"end\": 1874, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ineos\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"performance\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1831}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I wanted more autonomy, more ability to action my ideas.\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1954, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more ability\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 1934}, {\"ngram\": \"my ideas\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 1953}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I wasn't really getting that at Ineos.\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 1997, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1991, \"end\": 1996, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ineos\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The latest race content, interviews, features, reviews and expert buying guides, direct to your inbox!\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2101, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The latest race content\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2022}, {\"ngram\": \"interviews\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2034}, {\"ngram\": \"features\", \"from\": 2036, \"to\": 2044}, {\"ngram\": \"reviews\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2053}, {\"ngram\